{"tid":1368971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察入一入嚟 就算全世界遺棄你 我地都會全力支持你！！","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T20:44:17.000Z","uid":206787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9f77a5bb99cec9300ef9e046347280dd682d1f","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"我相信各位聽完張建宗呢條仆街嘅記者會都會無名火起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係估唔到你地一路盡心盡力，係前線拼搏，無論比人起底,比人沖擊，比人侮辱，都一直緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n但勢估唔到張建宗呢條仆街竟然同你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">割席</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n你要記著張建宗唔係代表一個人，係代表整個政府高層，姐係依家成個政府都對你地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用完即棄</span></span>，當你地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">comdom仔</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下你地係前線用命拼，盡忠職守，而班高官就係到涼住冷氣，飲紅酒，當你地馬戲團咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n佢地有當你地係警隊咩，佢地當你地係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警犬</span></span>炸，幫佢地看下門口，心情唔好就會搵你地出氣。<br />\n<br />\n我呢就真係為你地覺得唔抵啦，做就做最辛苦，但換落嘅係比人背叛，比人割席。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2EzcnV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2EzcnV.png&h=55fd1c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX1au9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX1au9C.png&h=3d2fdd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以警隊要團結起來，要張建宗等一班高官道歉同落台。否則警隊會全面罷工，劈炮，甚至行出嚟遊行示威！！一齊爭取警隊應有嘅尊嚴同對待。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時你地班政府高官後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地將都會全力支持警隊嘅行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有警隊朋友，就轉發出去，叫佢地一齊罷工，爭取應有嘅福利同尊嚴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e654a25c9ffd94e173fd41e29b2742d964638b","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"入嚟一齊支持警察全面罷工，爭取應有尊嚴同待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e892e900a9b643c0ab23f34d41d54f49d775a83","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"一齊支持警察全面罷工，爭取應有尊嚴同待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8599d3aaa304ef6827a9bcf0e0aa181c5de6d75","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"一齊支持警察全面罷工，爭取應有尊嚴同待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34edde0bd7cd9bd824d6455acd1cae6ac4b1bbfc","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c92e33b8a14ef597aa2d7f73ae3bbdd95fbcbd9","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9730b967045928262cd8010ce45ff96483faaf02","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c847e702dc5c6b36a08f94fc2e9f8a33ec9c4cd","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71e9f0e50c737e37a2eff35794ca82cc50eac5d1","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0407ba6c7239027fadd5e362109aa48d9a1c55ca","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"469f363fc1baff3cf9fd8c258ccb3563d5b099be","tid":1368971,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0c9a77d2161755003569376f37c490914331ecd","tid":1368971,"uid":208702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-0